column2: SELECT    m.ra_#,m.dec_#, q.EW_Hb_#, q.Flux_Hb_#, q.redshift, p.lumdist into mydb.exclu_#_EW_flux_Hb_nov2#_# FROM MyDB.MyTable_# AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra_#, m.dec_#, #) AS n    JOIN PhotoObjall AS o ON n.objid=o.objid   JOIN emissionlinesport as q ON o.specobjid=q.specobjid   JOIN Photoz AS p ON p.objid=o.objid
